Score: 13
<strong>Yayoi Kusama solo exhibition</strong>
<strong>Arcadia Earth exhibit</strong>
<strong>Museum of the Dog</strong>
<strong>&#226;&#128;&#152;Mark Twain and the Holy Land&#226;&#128;&#153;&#160;</strong>
