<strong>&#226;&#128;&#152;City of Workers, City of Struggle: How Labor Movements Changed New York&#226;&#128;&#153;</strong>
<strong>&#226;&#128;&#152;The Colmar Treasure: A Medieval Jewish Legacy&#226;&#128;&#153;</strong>
<strong>&#226;&#128;&#152;Waterfront&#226;&#128;&#153;</strong>
<strong>&#226;&#128;&#152;Taking Care of Brooklyn: Stories of Sickness of Health&#226;&#128;&#153;</strong>
